Dark Star Tracker - developed by Simon Katan

For MOTA - Museum of Transitory Art Ljubljana

This is an OpenFrameworks tracking program which uses X-Box Kinect to detect pointing gestures in users without need for a calibration pose.

Dependencies:

OF 007
ofxControlPanel
ofxOpenNI - not the roxlu version (also I hacked it a little bit). I'll post details here eventually
ofxXmlSettings
ofxDirList

OpenNI/NITE - the standard install from the website

Platforms:
tested on MAC and LINUX Ubuntu Studio 11.04






